      <title>OCI 以 20 亿美元的价格将甲醇业务出售给 Methanex</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/oci-sells-methanol-business-to-methanex-in-2-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OCI NV 同意以超过 20 亿美元的价格将其甲醇业务出售给 Methanex Corp.，这是这家荷兰化学品公司出售资产以提高其价值的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/oci-sells-methanol-business-to-methanex-in-2-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
